Exercise - I: 
1. Create a partially encapsulated class with private variables and public methods and
 try to give read only and write only permissions using getters, setters methods

Exercise - II: 
Write a program to demonstrate exception handling concepts:
i. Write a program with ArithmeticException and ArrayIndexBoundsExceptions and handle using try and catch block
ii. Handle with multiple catch blocks
iii. Handle with catch block and finally block
iv. Throw an exception using throw keyword and throws keyword